episodes.title: The Tragic Story Of HEAVENS GATE.
episodes.description: Uncover the chilling tale of Heaven’s Gate, a cult led by Marshall Applewhite, in this gripping documentary. Explore the group’s history, beliefs, and the events that culminated in a shocking mass suicide. Delve into the charismatic leader’s life, the group’s evolution, and the media frenzy that ensued. Join us as we unravel the mysteries surrounding Heaven’s Gate and its tragic end. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling and needs support, please reach out to the Samaritans hotline. Remember, help is available, and you don’t have to face challenges alone. #Documentary #HeavensGate #CultHistory
